Description: GeoWordNet is a semantic resource built from the full integration of WordNet- GeoNames and the Italian part of MultiWordNet.GeoWordNet Public Dataset contains 3-698-238 entities- 3-698-237 part-of relations between entities- 334 concepts- 182 relations between concepts- 3-698-238 relations between instances and concepts- and 13-562 (English and Italian) alternative entity names.CC-BY licence- please refer to Giunchiglia- Fausto and Maltese- Vincenzo and Farazi- Feroz and Dutta- Biswanath. GeoWordNet: A Resource for Geo-spatial Applications. Technical Report DIT-09-071- Department of Information Engineering and Computer Science- University of Trento. In Proc. of 7th Extended Semantic Web Conference- ESWC 2010- Heraklion- Crete- Greece- pp. 121-136.
